definitions.definition: Of or relating to a nodule or nodules.
Possessing, composed of, or similar in form to nodules .
examples: Loose nodular deposits of gold metal are commonly referred to as nuggets.
The disease causes nodular black growths that may become pustular.

main_definition: Of or relating to a nodule or nodules.
